These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, tulip, marigold, zinnia
5 different games are played: domino, bridge, monopoly, poker, canasta
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, trike, van, snowmobile
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person who growstulip is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person who growszinnia is between the person driving the helicopter and the person playing canasta##2
12. the person driving the van is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Flower      | amaryllis        | daisy | zinnia     | tulip   | marigold |
| Game   | monopoly     | bridge      | poker | canasta   | domino    |
| Transport   | van  | helicopter     | motorbike | trike | snowmobile  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

