.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, dunhill, dannemann, bluemaster, siglo
5 different games are played: chess, domino, canasta, backgammon, scrabble
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, kiwi, potato, radish, plum
 1. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is between the person playing chess and the siglo-smoker##2
 6. the person eating radish is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 8. the person playing canasta is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Cigar   | siglo    | dunhill       | dannemann      | swisher | bluemaster        |
| Game   | scrabble   | domino     | chess    | backgammon  | canasta     |
| Food     | potato    | kiwi | plum | radish | nectarine |

