.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, montecristo, bolivar, fonseca, havana
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, british, dutch, japanese, russian
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, trike, car, boat
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the british##1
 2. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
 3. the japanese is in the middle##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the italian##1
 7. the russian is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the dutch is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is the fonseca-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the russian##1
13. the person driving the boat is between the havana-smoker and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Cigar   | havana  | montecristo | tiparillo | fonseca | bolivar        |
