.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, august, november, july, september
5 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, pony, mouse, frog
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, scientist, electrician, fisherman, bartender
 1. the scientist is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the bartender is between the fan of reggae and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the electrician##1
 7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the owner of the frog is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the dancer##1
11. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
12. the dancer is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Birthday          | september  | november     | july   | august     | october |
| Pet         | frog | goat    | pony  | mouse | rabbit   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Job   | scientist    | electrician | fisherman | bartender | dancer   |

