.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, lemonade, milk, mirinda
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, car, skateboard, taxi, airplane
There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, taxi, blood-red, turquise
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, cooking, magic-tricks, video-games
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person driving the helicopter##2
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda       | almond-milk   | lemonade      | juice    |
| Transport       | airplane | taxi        | helicopter       | skateboard       | car |
| Color        | turquise     | fuchsia        | blood-red | purple        | taxi  |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | cooking | dancing      | video-games | drawing  |

