House: wooden, craftsman, futuristic, victorian, colonial
 1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating kiwimelon##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is between the person watching zombie movies and the craftsman house##2
 7. the futuristic house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the victorian house is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the craftsman house##2
12. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
