.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, dahlia, rose, zinnia
There are 5 different favourite colors: emerald, pink, grey, coral, green
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, canadian, italian, chinese, pakistani
 1. the person who likes green is between the canadian and the person who likes pink##2
 2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsrose##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 5. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the canadian##1
 7. the mexican is on the right of the pakistani##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
11. the italian is between the person who likes grey and the person who growsdahlia##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Flower       | zinnia | bellflower | dahlia  | rose | daisy    |
| Color       | grey        | coral   | pink  | green   | emerald |
| Nationality   | chinese       | italian      | pakistani      | mexican | canadian  |

