.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, turtle, guinea-pig, dog
House: victorian, cottage, art-deco, cape-cod, ranch-style
There 5 different types of food: apricot, pumpkin, artichoke, pepper, onion
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the cottage house##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the art-deco house and the owner of the turtle##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the victorian house is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the owner of the dog and the person eating pumpkin##2
 7. the person eating pepper is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the person eating apricot is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the art-deco house##1
11. the owner of the turtle is the cottage house##1
12. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Pet           | lizard | turtle | guinea-pig | dog    | chinchilla  |
| House   | cape-cod  | cottage    | victorian | art-deco    | ranch-style |
| Food   | artichoke  | pumpkin        | apricot   | pepper    | onion     |

