City: marseilles, miami, hannover, paris, venice
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, blues, gospel, dubstep, classical
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 4. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person traveling to marseilles and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is between the fan of techno and the dunhill-smoker##2
 8. the baccarat-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the dannemann-smoker##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
