.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, monopoly, colonial-climbing, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, february, march, october, december
House: townhouse, cape-cod, art-deco, gothic-revival, colonial
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the malaysian and the colonial house##2
 3. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is the townhouse house##1
 5. the townhouse house is between the thai and the art-deco house##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the person playing colonial-climbing is the cape-cod house##1
 9. the american is the cape-cod house##1
10. the person playing colonial-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | monopoly    | mah-jongg  | backgammon  | snooker      | colonial-climbing |
| Birthday   | february    | december   | october | march | january   |
| House   | art-deco | townhouse    | colonial    | gothic-revival       | cape-cod         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 